{
  "id": "6a1c32b072961886a54b6bcd",
  "title": "helpfeel/cosense-cli",
  "created": 1780232882,
  "updated": 1780235552,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a1c32b072961886a54b6bcd",
      "text": "helpfeel/cosense-cli",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780232882,
      "updated": 1780232882
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c32ba000000000030ec2b",
      "text": "公式[Cosense CLI]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780232890,
      "updated": 1780232894
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c32b2000000000030ec29",
      "text": "[helpfeel/cosense-cli: Cosenseのページを読み・調べ・編集する為のCLIとAgent Skillのリリースリポジトリ https://github.com/helpfeel/cosense-cli]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780232882,
      "updated": 1780232885
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3412000000000030ec2e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233234,
      "updated": 1780233638
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3559000000000030ec7c",
      "text": "インストール (Agent Skill)",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233561,
      "updated": 1780233635
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c355b000000000030ec7d",
      "text": " Claude Code",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233563,
      "updated": 1780233572
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c355c000000000030ec7e",
      "text": "  $ /plugin marketplace add helpfeel/cosense-cli",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233564,
      "updated": 1780233611
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c355c000000000030ec7f",
      "text": "  $ /plugin install cosense-cli@cosense-cli",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233564,
      "updated": 1780233611
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c355c000000000030ec80",
      "text": " Codex",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233564,
      "updated": 1780233574
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c355c000000000030ec81",
      "text": "  $ $skill-installer https://github.com/helpfeel/cosense-cli",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233564,
      "updated": 1780233612
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3424000000000030ec4d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233252,
      "updated": 1780233252
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c35a9000000000030ec82",
      "text": "インストール (CLI)",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233641,
      "updated": 1780233643
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c35c0000000000030ec86",
      "text": " > Skillの実行にはCLIが必要です",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233663,
      "updated": 1780233665
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c35ac000000000030ec83",
      "text": " $ npm install -g @helpfeel/cosense-cli",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233644,
      "updated": 1780233649
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c35b2000000000030ec85",
      "text": " $ cosense --help",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233649,
      "updated": 1780233653
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c35ac000000000030ec84",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233644,
      "updated": 1780233644
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3424000000000030ec4e",
      "text": "コマンド",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233252,
      "updated": 1780233254
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3412000000000030ec2f",
      "text": " `cosense <command> [args...]` ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233234,
      "updated": 1780233281
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3412000000000030ec31",
      "text": " 認証・アカウント",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233234,
      "updated": 1780233340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec66",
      "text": "  `login <origin|projectUrl>`: [Cosense Personal Access Token] または [Service Account] を設定ファイルに保存する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780234396
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c39be000000000030ec8c",
      "text": "   `<origin>`: Cosenseサーバーのorigin（例: https://scrapbox.io ）",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780234686,
      "updated": 1780234711
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c39be000000000030ec8d",
      "text": "   `<projectUrl>`: プロジェクトURL（例: https://scrapbox.io/Nota ）",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780234686,
      "updated": 1780234712
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3a53000000000030ec8e",
      "text": "   設定ファイル: [~/.cosense/settings.json]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780234835,
      "updated": 1780234848
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3a96000000000030ec8f",
      "text": "   環境変数[COSENSE_PAT]があれば設定ファイルより優先される",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780234902,
      "updated": 1780234918
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec67",
      "text": "  `whoami <origin>`: 現在の認証ユーザーの情報を取得する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780234402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec68",
      "text": "  `listProjects <origin>`: 自分が参加しているprojectの一覧を取得する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780234477
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec69",
      "text": "  `readProjectMembers <projectUrl>`: プロジェクトのメンバー一覧を取得する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780234482
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec6a",
      "text": " ページを読む",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780233340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec6b",
      "text": "  `browsePage <pageUrl>`: 単一ページを読む（markdown形式）",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780235552
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3b4f000000000030ec90",
      "text": "   メタデータ + アイコン記法 + テロメア + 本文をAIが読みやすい形式で出力する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780235087,
      "updated": 1780235544
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3b5d000000000030ec91",
      "text": "   行permalink `#<lineId>` 付きなら該当行をマーク",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780235101,
      "updated": 1780235104
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3d0a000000000030ec97",
      "text": "  `readPage <pageUrl>`: 単一ページを読む（JSON形式）",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780235530,
      "updated": 1780235536
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec6d",
      "text": "  `listPages <projectUrl> [options]`: プロジェクトのページ一覧を取得する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780234495
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec6e",
      "text": " 関連ページをたどる（リンクグラフ探索）",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780233340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec6f",
      "text": "  `browseRelatedPages <pageUrl>`: 1-hop + 2-hopの関連ページタイトル一覧をAIが読みやすい形式で出力する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780234501
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec70",
      "text": "  `list1hopLinks <pageUrl>`: 1-hop近傍を取得する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780234504
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec71",
      "text": "  `list2hopLinks <pageUrl>`: 2-hop近傍を取得する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780234508
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec72",
      "text": "  `search1hopLinks <pageUrl> <query>`: 1-hop近傍を全文検索でフィルタする",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780234518
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec73",
      "text": "  `search2hopLinks <pageUrl> <query>`: 2-hop近傍を全文検索でフィルタする",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780234519
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec74",
      "text": " 検索する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780233340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec75",
      "text": "  `searchFullText <projectUrl> <query>`: 本文全文を対象に検索する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780234525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec76",
      "text": "  `searchVector <projectUrl> <query>`: ベクトル検索でページを探す（タイトル＋本文中リンク記法のみ対象）",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780234528
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec77",
      "text": " ページを編集する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780233340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec78",
      "text": "  `previewEdit`: ページ編集opsをdry-runして `previewId` を取得する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780234555
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c393c000000000030ec88",
      "text": "   `previewEdit <projectUrl> <pageId>`: 既存ページ編集",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780234556,
      "updated": 1780234574
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3957000000000030ec89",
      "text": "   `previewEdit --new <projectUrl>`: 新規ページ作成",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780234583,
      "updated": 1780234588
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c347c000000000030ec79",
      "text": "  `submitEdit <projectUrl> <previewId>`: `previewEdit` で取得した `previewId` を使ってページ編集を確定する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233340,
      "updated": 1780234596
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3412000000000030ec4a",
      "text": "  `previewEdit` でdry-run → 内容確認 → `submitEdit` で確定、という2段階の安全な流れになっている[Claude.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233234,
      "updated": 1780233784
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3982000000000030ec8a",
      "text": "  [Cosense Personal Access Token]認証限定、Service Accountは不可",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780234626,
      "updated": 1780234648
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c3412000000000030ec4b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780233234,
      "updated": 1780233730
    }
  ]
}